<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听见了吗？这是国王的命令！”国王的手下喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“关上你们的窗户，锁上你们的门。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天贝德拉公主会经过这些街道，到达澡堂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有人都不准看她！违令者格杀勿论！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁在听到这些话之后跑回家了吗？没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贝德拉公主。”他叹气道，“每个人都觉得她一定非常美丽。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没错。她非常美丽。但是只有几个人看见过她的脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每当贝德拉公主离开宫殿时，她总是带着面纱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每次她去澡堂时都会引起骚动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家快离开这条街！”一个带红帽子的人大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回家！”一个老妇人大叫，“或者藏在你们的商店里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁站在街上，商人和顾客推挤着经过他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定要看到公主的脸。”阿拉丁做了决定。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说她的眼睛特别幽深，就像夜晚的天空一样黑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快阿拉丁成了唯一一个留在街上的人，突然他听见街角传来笛子的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“肯定是公主和她的随从来了。”阿拉丁说道，“我得快点儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑进澡堂，飞快地躲在门后面。时间刚刚好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁听到一些说话声，其中一个声音要比其他声音更加甜美。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在热气中蒸一蒸肯定非常好。”这个声音说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主进入澡堂之后，阿拉丁从门后面探出头来，正好看见贝德拉公主把面纱摘下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”阿拉丁小声说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见了她幽深黑亮的眼睛，她的微笑，她的红唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不能呼吸，也不能动了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道什么是美。”他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我知道贝德拉公主一定是这个世界上最美丽的女孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那一刻，他爱上了国王的女儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人看见阿拉丁从澡堂后门出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他回到家之后，他妈妈问：“怎么这么快就回来了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁没有回答。他坐在垫子上望着天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吃点儿东西。”泽巴说。她在他面前摆了点面包和干果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看起来不太好。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给他倒了一杯浓咖啡，但是阿拉丁什么都没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么了？”她问，“怎么不跟我说话？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您就让我一个人呆着吧。”阿拉丁回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他吃了一口面包，就回自己房间了。他整夜没能入睡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，阿拉丁还是没有动。泽巴很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不舒服吗？”她说，“我请个医生过来？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没生病，”他喃喃自语道，“我爱上一个人了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爱上一个人！”他妈妈惊喜地叫道，“哎呀，我的儿子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个幸运的女孩儿是谁啊？快点儿告诉我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爱上了贝德拉公主。”阿拉丁冷静地说，“我要跟她结婚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的妈妈惊讶地看着他，然后哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟国王的女儿结婚？你？一个裁缝的儿子？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”阿拉丁平静地说，“我要跟公主结婚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴抱头大叫：“我儿子疯了！精灵把他弄疯了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>